{"tid":2357033,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"督察譚健燊作供屢避答是否片中人 遇官質疑立即確認身份 惹旁聽人士訕笑","createTime":"2021-01-07T07:21:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-07T14:27:55.000Z","uid":240362,"like":298,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"e62d98788670c033079df8e0c6199c770b7500b3","tid":2357033,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T07:21:30.000Z","msg":"作供督察譚健燊（後方戴眼鏡者）:<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Wj7EFALrlHcX2ywRAZB85VPFnjY=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/V755NDCFPRFILF5XTFX4KQOZ3U.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FWj7EFALrlHcX2ywRAZB85VPFnjY%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FV755NDCFPRFILF5XTFX4KQOZ3U.JPG&h=136d148e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n示威者前年10月31日在多區集會，有文員疑遭警員追捕期間拳打警員，及後有網媒女記者嘗試舉手分隔二人，結果文員與記者分別被控襲警及阻差辦公罪，案件今續審，一度供稱女記者「令我追截慢咗一秒鐘嘅反應時間」的涉案督察繼續作供。庭上播放當晚現場情況片段，督察多次以影像模糊「睇唔到」為由，迴避作答當時是否身處片中。裁判官張天雁忍不住稱：「唔好不停話睇唔到，咁樣冇意思㗎。」督察最終表示：「法官閣下，我相信呢個係我本人。」<br />\n<br />\n庭上再度播放當晚多部警車趕到現場的片段，辯方問到閉路電視片段中有人從警車車頭位置下車，那人是否督察譚健燊本人；譚卻多次以影像模糊「睇唔到」為由作回應。<br />\n<br />\n譚的回答引來裁判官張天雁出言謂：「幫辦，你咁樣幫唔到法庭㗎。」張官續指：「你可以話可能係我，唔好不停話睇唔到，咁樣冇意思㗎。」張官又謂：「辯方大律師咁問你，係合理㗎&hellip;&hellip;你唔使勞氣，講證據就得㗎喇。」譚隨即謂：「法官閣下，我相信呢個係我本人。」<br />\n<br />\n此時公眾席傳來笑聲，張官即問：「邊個笑呀？」一名中年男子站立直言「係我笑」，並自行離座準備離開。張官見狀謂：「你認錯道歉就得㗎喇。」該男子謂：「我道歉，但我冇錯，因為笑係人嘅自然反應，係忍唔住嘅。」張官再說：「咁你出去啦，你嘅忍耐能力咁低。」惟男子邊行邊自辯說：「我出去，但我一啲都唔低。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210107/BEJYPMCY2NCSXDSND63VWOJZTE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210107%2FBEJYPMCY2NCSXDSND63VWOJZTE%2F&d=vTNdr7lgiRBdtcQZ4wg6z6GvShGfzVnrv2JJWMS0YvQ%3D&h=12380eb4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210107%2FBEJYPMCY2NCSXDSND63VWOJZTE%2F&h=ef924bec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210107/BEJYPMCY2NCSXDSND63VWOJZTE/</a>"},{"pid":"15bb40dde6efaefb0ba4c3be77e4b2ed01814791","tid":2357033,"uid":16061,"like":299,"dislike":0,"score":299,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T07:27:21.000Z","msg":"個中年男子有擔戴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8bc36e0432890a17f4b1404abc1403c9f2e810b","tid":2357033,"uid":78732,"like":139,"dislike":0,"score":139,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T07:28:33.000Z","msg":"旁聽師典範<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da76143b2201a5da4c910964ab026afc506ef09a","tid":2357033,"uid":345353,"like":50,"dislike":0,"score":50,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T07:33:13.000Z","msg":"忍笑師召喚"},{"pid":"d45e8fdd4c4a5afa085af685e04e521a3eda3a6e","tid":2357033,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T07:44:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92c7e607e4d607105253cb829d9c6692cc73ca8f","tid":2357033,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T07:45:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8947ceaf7a9d3b34f500639bd2fa9ed6ffbc6e0e","tid":2357033,"uid":2110,"like":205,"dislike":0,"score":205,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T07:47:36.000Z","msg":"此時公眾席傳來笑聲，張官即問：「邊個笑呀？」一名中年男子站立直言「係我笑」，並自行離座準備離開。張官見狀謂：「你認錯道歉就得㗎喇。」該男子謂：「我道歉，但我冇錯，因為笑係人嘅自然反應，係忍唔住嘅。」張官再說：「咁你出去啦，你嘅忍耐能力咁低。」惟男子邊行邊自辯說：「我出去，但我一啲都唔低。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f63cb3350adfc932a1e480e28334485d25b33b37","tid":2